{"tid":656144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日比個on9仔累撚死","createTime":"2018-05-07T03:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T04:45:09.000Z","uid":101303,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"07bc15400567fdae15376f250ef81967380ccd5b","tid":656144,"uid":101303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說今日group present 每人限講7分鐘 <br />\n<br />\n咁我果組就有個EQ有問題既組員 p.s老師分比我地<br />\n<br />\n到佢講果陣 條仆街同我講撚左十幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  本身超左1分鐘左右已經想stop 9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係見佢已經就快控制唔到自己(佢會好似痴線佬咁發癲，大叫扔野，分分鐘打9人)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我地唯有忍佢 成個presentation佢1999係到9up 係完全無內容 1分鐘講10個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後搞到我地超撚哂時 個doctor完全無心機聽佢or其他人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個presentation仲要佔成科30% 今鋪真係比佢累撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ad20ecb9c563adb65c1a2abf37a96ad984d527","tid":656144,"uid":40840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"樓主邊間u"},{"pid":"a499944b93e03c8939ad1f5b2c90c10dbc595446","tid":656144,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:41:29.000Z","msg":"有咩討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n篇野勁似facebook status<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f72ec5862bf2d417a832b30b57dd8b